_sText:
Map Name: de_witness

Author: Wintermute

Release Date: 2nd June 2006

Number of Spawn Points: 40

Screenshots, Download and Info:
http://www.twistedpuppy.co.uk/de_witness.html

OBJECTIVES:
The star witness is about to be moved from an anonymous safehouse down-town.
A few Counter-Terrorists are baby-sitting the witness
The rest have just arrived downstairs with transport.

COUNTER-TERRORISTS:
Protect the witness & stop the van that will take him to court from being destroyed.

TERRORISTS:
Kill the witness by detonating a bomb outside his room.
If this isn't possible then delay his court date by destroying the van downstairs.

INFO:

You can see loads of hi-res images and get the map from:
http://www.twistedpuppy.co.uk/de_witness.html

I've tried to thank the beta testers in the game's .txt file - everyone else who's provided feeback and help has a "thank you" on the website (apologies if I've forgotton anyone). 

Would be great if you've got the time to take a look and let me know what you think ...really pleased with the final map - hope you'll give it a try.

Cheers,
Wintermute

Next generation CS:S Maps:
http://www.twistedpuppy.co.uk
